</think>

<answer>
\begin{align}
(x+y+z)(x y+x z+y z)&=25 \\[10pt]
x y(x+y)+z(x y+x z+y z)&=25 \\[10pt]
7(x+y z)&=25 \\[10pt]
x y z&=\dfrac{7}{3}
\end{align}
</answer>

